contentfulProduct.title: Modal Jersey Lounge Jogger

content.value: Just about the comfiest joggers around. The smooth, elastic waistband and banded cuff ensure an ideal fit. Great to lounge or even sleep in.
Elastic waistband for an easier and comfortable fit
Two front pockets
Made using eco-friendly dyes resulting in less water consumption
Produced in SA8000 certified factories which aims to improve working conditions throughout the supply chain
Material: 95% Modal/ 5% Spandex
Origin: Jiangsu, China
Model is 5'9" and wearing a size Small
Machine wash cold. Gentle cycle with like colors. Do not bleach. Tumble dry low. Low iron if necessary. Do not dry clean.
